description: Midsona AB engages in the manufacture and distribution of health and well-being products. The company is headquartered in Malmo, Skane and currently employs 831 full-time employees.  Its products are divided into three product areas: Healthfoods, Hygiene, Personal Care. The firm consists of three geographical areas, namely Sweden, Norway and Finland. The business areas in Sweden, Norway and Finland market and sell nutritional supplements, herbal remedies, health foods, skin care and beauty products to grocery stores, pharmacies and health stores in respective geographic markets. The firm has several priority brands, such as Friggs, Urtekram, Naturdiet, Miwana, MyggA, Dalblads, Tri Tolonen, Supernature.
name: Midsona AB
